\">WindowsForum</a></div>\r\n            <div><a href=\"http://www.wired.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Wired</a></div>\r\n            <div><a href=\"http://www.zdnet.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">ZDnet</a></div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"simpleText\"></div>\r\n            \r\n                        </div>\r\n                        <a class=\"btn more_travel\" href=\"https://www.adpulsemedia.com/adpulse-media-features-technology/#section2\">More about the ad network </a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <!-- Section Three -->\r\n            <div class=\"travelNetwork centerAlign page_space scroll_a\" id=\"targetting\">\r\n                    <a href=\"#targetting\" class=\"scrollToTarget\">&nbsp;</a>\r\n                    <div class=\"wrapper\">\r\n                        <div class=\"targetTopSec\">\r\n                            <h3 class=\"mtitle\">Targeting</h3>\r\n                            <!-- <div class=\"borderSec\"></div> -->\r\n                            <div class=\"travelSec\">\r\n                                <!-- <div class=\"col-2 pull-right\">\r\n                                    <div class=\"primiumImage\">\r\n                                        <img src=\"\" alt=\"tragetting-img\">\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                </div> -->\r\n                                <div class=\"col-12\">\r\n                                    <div class=\"primiumContent\">\r\n                                        <h4>It starts with the right audience</h4>\r\n                <p>Reach and convert “in-market” buyers based on powerful online purchase intent signals. We turn data into ROI with the power of precise audience targeting.</p>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                \r\n                            <div class=\"targetingCategory\">\r\n                                <div class=\"pointtageting\">\r\n                                    <h3>Page Level Targeting</h3>\r\n                <p>Attract your desired audience at the exact moment they’re visiting tech sites, engaging with specific content related to your offer.</p>\r\n                <h3>Behavioral Targeting</h3>\r\n                <p>Reach people most likely to respond based on their keywords searched, browsing behavior, competitor site visits and content consumed.</p>\r\n                <h3>Custom Built Audiences</h3>\r\n                <p>Your customized ad campaign will target people identified as within your target audience &amp; actively researching the products or services you sell.</p>\r\n                                    \r\n                                </div>\r\n                                <div class=\"differntCate\">\r\n                                    <figure>\r\n                                        <img src=\"https://sdyeraq6z4if2sl-zippykid.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/Category-Technology.png\" alt=\"travel_img\">						\r\n                                    </figure>\r\n                                    <ul>\r\n                                        <li class=\"behavior\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\">Device: Mac						</a></li>\r\n                                        <li class=\"interests\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\">Location: USA</a></li>\r\n                                        <li class=\"demographics\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\">Behavior:  IT Buyer</a></li>\r\n                                        <li class=\"kaywords\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\">Keywords: Data Center</a></li>\r\n                                    </ul>\r\n                \r\n                                </div>\r\n                \r\n                            </div>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                 