 moment they’re visiting tech sites, engaging with specific content related to your offer.</p>\r\n                <h3>Behavioral Targeting</h3>\r\n                <p>Reach people most likely to respond based on their keywords searched, browsing behavior, competitor site visits and content consumed.</p>\r\n                <h3>Custom Built Audiences</h3>\r\n                <p>Your customized ad campaign will target people identified as within your target audience &amp; actively researching the products or services you sell.</p>\r\n                                    \r\n                                </div>\r\n                                <div class=\"differntCate\">\r\n                                    <figure>\r\n                                        <img src=\"https://sdyeraq6z4if2sl-zippykid.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/Category-Technology.png\" alt=\"travel_img\">						\r\n                                    </figure>\r\n                                    <ul>\r\n                                        <li class=\"behavior\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\">Device: Mac						</a></li>\r\n                                        <li class=\"interests\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\">Location: USA</a></li>\r\n                                        <li class=\"demographics\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\">Behavior:  IT Buyer</a></li>\r\n                                        <li class=\"kaywords\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\">Keywords: Data Center</a></li>\r\n                                    </ul>\r\n                \r\n                                </div>\r\n                \r\n                            </div>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        <div class=\"reachMarket\">\r\n                            <div class=\"primiumContent\">\r\n                                <h4 class=\"sbtitle\">Reach in-market audiences for:</h4>\r\n                \r\n                                <div class=\"discriptionField\">\r\n                                                            <div class=\"advertisingFor\">\r\n                                            <div class=\"col-3\">\r\n                                                <ul class=\"advantageList\">\r\n                                                    <li>App Dev</li><li>Antivirus</li><li>Apple Users</li><li>Brand Shoppers</li><li>Certification</li><li>Cloud Services</li><li>Computer Brands</li><li>Computer Games</li><li>Data Centers</li>								</ul>\r\n                                            </div>\r\n                                            <div class=\"col-3\">\r\n                                                <ul class=\"advantageList\">\r\n                                                    <li>Enterprise Tech Buyer</li><li>Hardware</li><li>Internet Services</li><li>Laptops &amp; Tablets</li><li>Mac Users</li><li>Mobile Tech</li><li>Networking</li><li>Parts &amp; Components</li><li>Peripherals</li>								</ul>\r\n                                            </div>\r\n                                            <div class=\"col-3\">\r\n                                                <ul class=\"advantageList\">\r\n                                                    <li>Reviews</li><li>Security &amp; Backup</li><li>Servers &amp; Networking</li><li>Smart Home</li><li>Software</li><li>Tech News</li><li>Tech Support</li><li>Web Services</li><li>Windows</li>								</ul>\r\n                                            </div>\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                        \r\n                \r\n                                    </div>\r\n                \r\n                \r\n                                    <div class=\"marketTableSec\">\r\n                                        <table width=\"100%\">\r\n                                            <tbody>\r\n                                                <tr>\r\n                                                    \r\n                                                    <!-- <td><img src=\"../wp-content/themes/adpulse_media/images/rightcheck.png\" alt=\"rightcheck-img\"></td> -->\r\n                \r\n                                                                                    </tr>\r\n                \r\n                                            </tbody>\r\n                                        </table>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    <a class=\"btn more_travel\" href=\"https://www.adpulsemedia.com/adpulse-media-features-technology/#section3\">More about targeting </a>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <!-- Section 4 -->\r\n                    <div class=\"travelNetwork centerAlign page_space greyback scroll_a\" id=\"retarGet\">\r\n							<a href=\"#retarGet\" class=\"scrollToTarget\">&nbsp;</a>\r\n							<div class=\"wrapper\">\r\n								<h3 class=\"mtitle\">Retargeting</h3>\r\n								<!-- <div class=\"borderSec\"></div> -->\r\n								<div class=\"travelSec\">\r\n									<!-- <div class=\"col-2 pull-right\">\r\n										<div class=\"primiumImage\">\r\n											<img src=\"\" alt=\"tragetting-img\">\r\n										</div>\r\n									</div> -->\r\n									<div class=\"col-12\">\r\n										<div class=\"primiumContent\">\r\n											<h4>Bring back past website visitors &amp; grow sales</h4>\r\n<p>You attract website visitors, but not all of them make a purchase.<br>\r\nTypically only 2% of website visitors convert on their first visit.</p>\r\n<p>Retargeting shows your ads on sites all across the web, but only to people<br>\r\nwho have previously visited your website and left without making a purchase.</p>\r\n										</div>\r\n									</div>\r\n								</div>\r\n								<div class=\"youbeni\">\r\n									<div class=\"worksBenifit mt0\">\r\n										<!-- <div class=\"col-2\">\r\n											<div class=\"howItWorks\">\r\n																							</div>\r\n										</div>\r\n\r\n										<div class=\"col-2\">\r\n											<div class=\"howItWorks\">\r\n																							</div>\r\n										</div> -->\r\n\r\n										<h6>How it works:</h6>\r\n										<ul>\r\n\r\n											\r\n										 				                                <li>\r\n													<img src=\"https://sdyeraq6z4if2sl-zippykid.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/howitwork-img.jpg\" alt=\"icon\">\r\n					                                <span>1</span>\r\n\r\n					                                 <p>People visit your website, but leave without making a purchase.</p>\r\n				                                 </li>\r\n				                        				                                <li>\r\n													<img src=\"https://sdyeraq6z4if2sl-zippykid.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/howitwork-img1.jpg\" alt=\"icon\">\r\n					                                <span>2</span>\r\n\r\n					                                 <p>Browsing the web, they see your<br>\r\nads wherever they go online.</p>\r\n				                                 </li>\r\n				                        				                                <li>\r\n													<img src=\"https://sdyeraq6z4if2sl-zippykid.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/howitwork-img2.jpg\" alt=\"icon\">\r\n					                                <span>3</span>\r\n\r\n					                                 <p>Interest is recaptured and they<br>\r\nrevisit your site to buy.</p>\r\n				                                 </li>\r\n				                        											\r\n										</ul>\r\n																				<div class=\"whyRetargeting\">\r\n											<div class=\"primiumContent\">\r\n												<h6>Why Retargeting?</h6>\r\n												<p>Proven to outperform all other online advertising strategies.<br>\r\nYou\'ll stay fresh in the minds of prospects until they’re ready to buy.</p>\r\n											</div>											\r\n\r\n											<di