(256, 1, '2018-06-06 10:56:12', '2018-06-06 10:56:12', '<header id=\"trade-header\" class=\"gtco-cover gtco-cover-sm tradeing_bg feature_bg\" role=\"banner\">\n        <div class=\"gtco-container\">\n            <div class=\"row\">\n                <div class=\"col-md-12 text-center\">\n                    <div class=\"display-t\">\n                        <div class=\"display-tc animate-box\" data-animate-effect=\"fadeIn\">\n                            <h1>Powerful Features</h1>\n                            <p>Everything you need for effective advertising. Everything included.</p>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n<div class=\"cl_wraper\">\n     <div class=\"spy-content-container\">\n                <div class=\"spy-content-row overview section1\" id=\"section-1\">\n                    <div class=\"wrapper\">\n                        <div class=\"spyMenuBox\">\n                            <ul class=\"nav\">\n                                <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#section1\">Overview</a></li>\n                                <li class=\"\"><a href=\"#section2\">Network</a></li><li class=\"\"><a href=\"#section3\">Targeting</a></li>\n                                <li class=\"\"><a href=\"#section4\">Retargeting</a></li>\n                                <li class=\"\"><a href=\"#section5\">Ad Design</a></li>\n                                <li class=\"\"><a href=\"#section6\">Mobile</a></li><li class=\"\"><a href=\"#section7\">More Features</a></li>\n                                <li class=\"\"><a href=\"#readyStart\">Get Started</a></li>\n                            </ul>\n                        </div>\n<h3 class=\"accordian-mobile\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0);\">Overview</a></h3>\n<div class=\"spy-content\" style=\"padding-top: 0px;\">\n<h3>Overview</h3><h4>You run your business. Leave the advertising to us.</h4><p>AdPulse Media makes it easy for travel advertisers of all types &amp; budgets to reach highly specific “in-market”<br>\naudiences that drive ad performance &amp; increases ROI.</p>\n<p>We deliver custom-built display advertising solutions by combining premium ad placements, precise audience targeting, engaging creative,&nbsp;effective retargeting, ongoing optimization and comprehensive reporting.</p>\n<p>Every&nbsp;ad campaign is fully managed -&nbsp;it’s all done for you.</p></div></div>\n                </div>               \n                <div id=\"sp-section-2\" class=\"spy-content-row full-section-sp section2\">\n                    <a href=\"#sp-section-2\" class=\"scrollToTarget\">&nbsp;</a>\n                    <div class=\"wrapper\">\n                        <h3 class=\"accordian-mobile\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0);\">Network</a></h3>\n                        <div class=\"spy-content network\">\n                        <h3>Network</h3><h4>Premium performance display advertising.</h4><p>To build your ad campaign, we carefully select ad placements across a network of hundreds of top sites,<br>\non pages with content that relates to your offer.</p>\n<p>Ads on premium sites perform better as they’re surrounded by quality content and reach well defined,<br>\nengaged audiences.</p>\n<p>With ads running across an entire network of relevant sites, there’s more opportunity to find your ideal<br>\naudience&nbsp;and drive engagement, brand awareness &amp; conversions.</p>\n<div class=\"listing-content\">\n<ul>\n<li>\n<h5>Custom-Built Ad Campaigns</h5>\n<p>Every business is different. That’s why we<br>\ncustom-build every ad campaign so it’s right for your brand, your offer, and your budget.</p></li>\n<li>\n<h5>Attract Buyers on Premium Sites</h5>\n<p>Get unrivaled access to a premium network<br>\nof the web\'s most trusted sites, and the<br>\nquality audiences they attract.</p></li>\n<li>\n<h5>Get Found on Every Device</h5>\n<p>Reach everyone, everywhere on any device.<br>\nYour ads can be delivered on desktops,<br>\ntablets and mobile phones.</p></li>\n<li>\n<h5>Above-the-Fold Ad Placement</h5>\n<p>Your ads are placed near the top of web<br>\npages and viewable without scrolling<br>\ndown to&nbsp;the bottom of a page.</p></li>\n<li>\n<h5>Real-Time Reporting</h5>\n<p>Get detailed insights into campaign performance. Log in 24/7 &amp; view fully transparent reporting. Learn what’s driving conversions.</p></li>\n<li>\n<h5>Campaign Optimization</h5>\n<p>For maximum performance, your campaign is monitored and adjusted for more exposure<br>\non the best performing sites and ad placements.</p></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>               \n<div id=\"sp-section-3\" class=\"spy-content-row full-section-sp section3\">\n<a href=\"#sp-section-3\" class=\"scrollToTarget\">&nbsp;</a>\n<div class=\"wrapper\">\n<h3 class=\"accordian-mobile\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0);\">Targeting</a></h3>\n<div class=\"spy-content network\">\n<h3>Targeting</h3><h4>A full suite of audience targeting solutions.</h4><p>We combine both behavioral targeting and page-level site targeting so your ads are not only placed near specific content on quality brand-safe&nbsp;sites, but also served across the web to people whose interests, demographics, search &amp; browsing behavior has identified them as within your target audience.</p>\n<p>We custom build your ad campaign using all of the targeting strategies required to meet your marketing goals.</p>\n<div class=\"listing-content\">\n<ul>\n<li>\n<h5>Page-Level&nbsp;Targeting</h5>\n<p>Your ads are delivered in real-time to highly engaged consumers at the exact moment they’re viewing content related to what you’re selling.</p></li>\n<li>\n<h5>In-Market Behavior</h5>\n<p>You\'ll connect with potential customers who are actively researching or shopping for the types of products or services you sell.</p></li>\n<li>\n<h5>Demographic Targeting</h5>\n<p>Choose to show your ads by any gender, age group, income level, language, ethnic groups<br>\nor life stage.</p></li>\n<li>\n<h5>Location Targeting</h5>\n<p>Your ads will be shown only where you do business. Zero in by country, state, city or town,<br>\nzip codes, or DMA.</p></li>\n<li>\n<h5>Keyword Targeting</h5>\n<p>The words people type into search engines are by far the most important indicator of purchase intent. Target prospects based on keywords searched.</p></li>\n<li>\n<h5>Purchase Intent</h5>\n<p>Find new customers across the web who have visited competitor sites and who demonstrate powerful purchase intent signals.</p></li>\n</ul>\n</div></div></div></div>\n<div id=\"sp-section-4\" class=\"spy-content-row full-section-sp section4\">\n<a href=\"#sp-section-4\" class=\"scrollToTarget\">&nbsp;</a>\n<div class=\"wrapper\">\n<h3 class=\"accordian-mobile\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0);\">Retargeting</a></h3>\n <div class=\"spy-content network\">\n<h3>Retargeting</h3><h4>Bring back past website visitors. Increase conversions.</h4><p>Retargeting is the most effective way to grow sales online. You’ll bring back your past website visitors as they<br>\nsee your ads while browsing other sites across the web. Before you know it, they’re back on your website<br>\nto make a purchase.</p>\n<p>We can include retargeting as part of your ad campaign or you can run a retargeting campaign on its own.</p>\n<div class=\"listing-content\">\n<ul>\n<li>\n<h5>Target Specific Customers</h5>\n<p>Run a retargeting campaign for different products or services or for users who visited certain pages on your site.</p></li>\n<li>\n<h5>Un-Target Your Buyers</h5>\n<p>You can “un-target” visitors who have already signed-up or made a purchase &amp; don’t need to see your ads again.</p></li>\n<li>\n<h5>Build Your Brand</h5>\n<p>Retargeting makes you seem much bigger as your ads seem to follow users &amp; appear “everywhere” across the web.</p></li>\n<li>\n<h5>Reach Valuable Prospects</h5>\n<p>Reach people who have already expressed interest in your services as they consider their purchase options.</p></li>\n<li>\n<h5>Enhanced&nbsp;Retargeting</h5>\n<p>We “follow the data” to retarget those&nbsp;site visitors most likely to convert based on their&nbsp;off-site&nbsp;purchase intent signals.</p></li>\n<li>\n<h5>Get Proven Results</h5>\n<p>Retargeted visitors are 70% more likely to convert on a website after being exposed to repeated retargeting ads.</p></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<p><em>For retargeting, we’ll provide a small snippet of code for you to place on your website. This has no effect on your site<br>\nexcept to “cookie” visitors for retargeting ads across the web.</em></p>\n</div></div></div>               \n<div id=\"sp-section-5\" class=\"spy-content-row full-section-sp section5\">\n<a href=\"#sp-section-5\" class=\"scrollToTarget\">&nbsp;</a>\n<div class=\"wrapper\">\n<h3 class=\"accordian-mobile\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0);\">Ad Design</a></h3>\n<div class=\"spy-content network\">\n<h3>Ad Design</h3><h4>Get ad creative that converts.</h4><p>We design your banner ads to match your website style, branding &amp; logo, images, ad copy &amp; appropriate<br>\ncall-to-action.</p>\n<p>Our ad design process follows marketing best practices, which aligns your ads with the content on the<br>\nlanding&nbsp;pages that the ads direct to, providing a seamless user experience.</p>\n<div class=\"listing-content\">\n<ul>\n<li>\n<h5>Experienced Design Team</h5>\n<p>Get 100% custom designed ads that match your brand. No templates or automated “ad builders”<br>\nare used.</p></li>\n<li>\n<h5>Save on Design Costs</h5>\n<p>Great ad design can cost hundreds of dollars.<br>\nGet professional ad design included with your ad campaign.</p></li>\n<li>\n<h5>Revision &amp; Modification</h5>\n<p>Not totally happy? We’ll do any changes needed to get your ads just right! Your ads only go live after your approval.</p></li>\n<li>\n<h5>A / B Split Testing</h5>\n<p>Increase conversions and learn what performs best. Split test different messages, images, colors, fonts, buttons, etc.</p></li>\n<li>\n<h5>Display Ads Work</h5>\n<p>Display advertising is predicted to overtake search as the top online ad segment because targeted display ads work great!</p></li>\n<li>\n<h5>Use Your Own Creatives</h5>\n<p>Have your own banner ads already tested &amp; ready to go? No problem. We can run your ads, our design version or both.</p></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"addSpecs\">\n<div class=\"cell cell-1\">\n<h5>Ad Specs:</h5>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell cell-2\">\n<h5>Banner ad sizes:</h5>\n<p>300x250, 728x90, 160x600, 300x600<br>\n320x50 (mobile), 300x50 (mobile)</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell cell-3\">\n<h5>Formats:</h5>\n<p>JPG, GIF,<br>\nPNG, HTML5</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell cell-4\">\n<h5>File size:</h5>\n<p>Up to<br>\n150 KB</p>\n</div>\n</div></div></div></div>\n<div id=\"sp-section-6\" class=\"spy-content-row full-section-sp section6\">\n<a href=\"#sp-section-6\" class=\"scrollToTarget\">&nbsp;</a>\n<div class=\"wrapper\"><h3 class=\"accordian-mobile\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0);\">Mobile</a></h3>\n<div class=\"spy-content network\">\n<h3>Mobile</h3><h4>High performance mobile advertising.</h4><p>Reach engaged consumers on their mobile phones and tablets with highly targeted advertising&nbsp;across<br>\nthe mobile web.</p>\n<p>We combine data-driven, intent-based targeting with demographics, location, device, &amp; online purchase intent signals to build your mobile ad campaign.&nbsp;You can run some of your ads, or an entire campaign on mobile.</p>\n<div class=\"listing-content\">\n<ul>\n<li>\n<h5>Precise Mobile&nbsp;Audiences</h5>\n<p>Reach consumers on their mobile devices based on&nbsp;user interest &amp; purchase intent signals gathered across devices.</p></li>\n<li>\n<h5>Data-Driven Targeting</h5>\n<p>Our data-enhanced targeting allows you to pinpoint the right audience based on multiple purchase intent&nbsp;signals.</p></li>\n<li>\n<h5>Geo-Fencing</h5>\n<p>Using GPS technology, we can display your mobile ads within any pre-defined radius around any specified location.</p></li>\n<li>\n<h5>Target Any Device</h5>\n<p>Access mobile users on any &nbsp;or all types of mobile devices: iPhone, iPad, Android, Blackberry and Windows Mobile.</p></li>\n<li>\n<h5>Location Affinities</h5>\n<p>Audience data can show which locations show the highest propensity towards your offer – down to the zip code level!</p></li>\n<li>\n<h5>Mobile Ad Design</h5>\n<p>We can design your ads specifically for mobile performance, which is different from desktop display ad design.</p></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div></div></div>\n<div id=\"sp-section-7\" class=\"spy-content-row full-section-sp section7\">\n<a href=\"#sp-section-7\" class=\"scrollToTarget\">&nbsp;</a>\n<div class=\"wrapper\">\n<h3 class=\"accordian-mobile\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0);\">More Features</a></h3>\n<div class=\"spy-content network\">\n<h3>More Features</h3><h4>Every ad campaign includes these built-in features.</h4><p>You’ll get more out of your marketing as our digital advertising experts collaborate with you to understand your business, your offer, your target audience and your marketing goals.</p>\n<p>We set up and fully manage your ad campaign, delivering expertise, strategy and support every step of the way.</p>\n<div class=\"listing-content\">\n<ul>\n<li>\n<h5>Flat-Rate Pricing</h5>\n<p>All ad campaigns are purchased for a simple flat-rate price. Everything is included so you’ll always know your exact cost upfront.</p></li>\n<li>\n<h5>Campaign Management</h5>\n<p>It’s all done for you. From audience targeting to ad design to ad placement and optimization, there’s no effort or work you’ll need to do.</p></li>\n<li>\n<h5>Dedicated Account Manager</h5>\n<p>You’ll have a single point of contact so you can always speak to an account manager who’s familiar with your campaign.</p></li>\n<li>\n<h5>Brand Safety</h5>\n<p>Protect the integrity of your brand with our hand vetted, pre-approved publisher sites, plus 3rd-party ad verification to ensure quality.</p></li>\n<li>\n<h5>Real-Time Reporting</h5>\n<p>Get detailed insights into campaign performance. Log in 24 / 7 &amp; view all the sites where your ads appear, impressions, clicks, CTR &amp; more.</p></li>\n<li>\n<h5>No Long-Term Contracts</h5>\n<p>There\'s no long-term contract or obligation beyond your purchased ad plan. See good results, come back and scale up for more!</p></li>\n</ul>\n</div></div></div></div>\n<!-- <div id=\"sp-sec-service\" class=\"spy-content-row full-section-sp section8\">	\n<a href=\"#sp-sec-service\" class=\"scrollToTarget\">&nbsp;</a>\n<div class=\"wrapper\">\n<h3 class=\"accordian-mobile\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0);\">READY TO GET STARTED?</a></h3>\n<div class=\"spy-content sp-features\">\n<div class=\"travelNetwork page_space mobileAD centerAlign readyto\" id=\"getStarted\">\n<h3>Ready to Get Started?</h3>\n<div class=\"borderSec\"></div>\n<div class=\"readyStart\">\n<div class=\"col-2\">\n<div class=\"Startedbox\">\n<h2>Self-Serve</h2><p><img class=\" size-full wp-image-5477 aligncenter\" src=\"https://sdyeraq6z4if2sl-zippykid.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/self-server.png\" alt=\"self-server\" width=\"91\" height=\"68\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Book an ad campaign through our self-serve advertising platform.</p>\n<p>Plans from <strong>$500 - $2500</strong></p>\n<p>Following sign-up, we’ll contact you to discuss all of the details before your ads go live.</p>\n<p><a class=\"btn get-started\" href=\"#\">get started</a></p></div></div>\n<div class=\"col-2\">\n<div class=\"Startedbox\">\n<h2>Contact Sales</h2><p><img class=\" size-full wp-image-5478 aligncenter\" src=\"https://sdyeraq6z4if2sl-zippykid.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/contact-salse.png\" alt=\"contact-salse\" width=\"92\" height=\"70\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>For custom solutions or larger ad campaigns, contact our sales team.</p>\n<p>Call us: <strong>1-800- 642-6912</strong></p>\n<p>Let’s discuss your advertising requirements. Get a no-obligation, customized proposal.</p>\n<p><a class=\"btn get-started\" href=\"#\">Get in Touch</a></p>\n</div></div></div></div></div></div>\n</div> -->\n<div id=\"readyStart\" class=\"readyStart page_space\" style=\"background-image: url(\'https://www.adpulsemedia.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/liburan-keluarga.png\');\">\n<div class=\"wrapper\">\n<div class=\"readystartinner\">\n<h3 class=\"mtitle\">Ready to get Started?</h3>\n<p>Call us: <a href=\"tel:18006426912\">1-800-642-6912</a></p>\n<p>Let’s discuss your advertising requirements.</p>\n<p>Get a no-obligation, customized proposal.</p>\n<div class=\"readyFormWrap\">\n<div role=\"form\" class=\"wpcf7\" id=\"wpcf7-f5615-o1\" lang=\"en-US\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<div class=\"screen-reader-response\"></div>\n\n</div></div></div></div></div></div></div>', 'Media Features', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '241-autosave-v1', '', '', '2018-06-06 10:56:12', '2018-06-06 10:56:12', '', 241, 'http://localhost/medias/2018/06/06/241-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
