                               </div>\r\n                \r\n                \r\n                                    <div class=\"marketTableSec\">\r\n                                        <table width=\"100%\">\r\n                                            <tbody>\r\n                                                <tr>\r\n                                                    \r\n                                                    <!-- <td><img src=\"../wp-content/themes/adpulse_media/images/rightcheck.png\" alt=\"rightcheck-img\"></td> -->\r\n                \r\n                                                                                    </tr>\r\n                \r\n                                            </tbody>\r\n                                        </table>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    <a class=\"btn more_travel\" href=\"https://www.adpulsemedia.com/adpulse-media-features-technology/#section3\">More about targeting </a>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <!-- Section 4 -->\r\n                    <div class=\"travelNetwork centerAlign page_space greyback scroll_a\" id=\"retarGet\">\r\n							<a href=\"#retarGet\" class=\"scrollToTarget\">&nbsp;</a>\r\n							<div class=\"wrapper\">\r\n								<h3 class=\"mtitle\">Retargeting</h3>\r\n								<!-- <div class=\"borderSec\"></div> -->\r\n								<div class=\"travelSec\">\r\n									<!-- <div class=\"col-2 pull-right\">\r\n										<div class=\"primiumImage\">\r\n											<img src=\"\" alt=\"tragetting-img\">\r\n										</div>\r\n									</div> -->\r\n									<div class=\"col-12\">\r\n										<div class=\"primiumContent\">\r\n											<h4>Bring back past website visitors &amp; grow sales</h4>\r\n<p>You attract website visitors, but not all of them make a purchase.<br>\r\nTypically only 2% of website visitors convert on their first visit.</p>\r\n<p>Retargeting shows your ads on sites all across the web, but only to people<br>\r\nwho have previously visited your website and left without making a purchase.</p>\r\n										</div>\r\n									</div>\r\n								</div>\r\n								<div class=\"youbeni\">\r\n									<div class=\"worksBenifit mt0\">\r\n										<!-- <div class=\"col-2\">\r\n											<div class=\"howItWorks\">\r\n																							</div>\r\n										</div>\r\n\r\n										<div class=\"col-2\">\r\n											<div class=\"howItWorks\">\r\n																							</div>\r\n										</div> -->\r\n\r\n										<h6>How it works:</h6>\r\n										<ul>\r\n\r\n											\r\n										 				                                <li>\r\n													<img src=\"https://sdyeraq6z4if2sl-zippykid.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/howitwork-img.jpg\" alt=\"icon\">\r\n					                                <span>1</span>\r\n\r\n					                                 <p>People visit your website, but leave without making a purchase.</p>\r\n				                                 </li>\r\n				                        				                                <li>\r\n													<img src=\"https://sdyeraq6z4if2sl-zippykid.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/howitwork-img1.jpg\" alt=\"icon\">\r\n					                                <span>2</span>\r\n\r\n					                                 <p>Browsing the web, they see your<br>\r\nads wherever they go online.</p>\r\n				                                 </li>\r\n				                        				                                <li>\r\n													<img src=\"https://sdyeraq6z4if2sl-zippykid.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/howitwork-img2.jpg\" alt=\"icon\">\r\n					                                <span>3</span>\r\n\r\n					                                 <p>Interest is recaptured and they<br>\r\nrevisit your site to buy.</p>\r\n				                                 </li>\r\n				                        											\r\n										</ul>\r\n																				<div class=\"whyRetargeting\">\r\n											<div class=\"primiumContent\">\r\n												<h6>Why Retargeting?</h6>\r\n												<p>Proven to outperform all other online advertising strategies.<br>\r\nYou\'ll stay fresh in the minds of prospects until they’re ready to buy.</p>\r\n											</div>											\r\n\r\n											<div class=\"aboutRetargeting\">\r\n												<div class=\"websiteTraffic\">\r\n													<span><sup>+</sup>726<sub>%</sub></span>\r\n													<h3>GROW WEBSITE TRAFFIC</h3>\r\n<p>Studies show an average 726% increase in<br>\r\nwebsite visits vs advertising without retargeting<br>\r\nafter four weeks of retargeted ad exposure.</p>\r\n												</div>\r\n												<div class=\"increaseConver\">\r\n													<span><sup>+</sup>70<sub>%</sub></span>\r\n													<h3>INCREASE CONVERSIONS</h3>\r\n<p>Your retargeted website visitors are 70% more<br>\r\nlikely to convert after being exposed to repeated<br>\r\nonline retargeting ads.</p>\r\n												</div>\r\n											</div>\r\n											<span class=\"source\">Source:comScore</span>\r\n										</div>\r\n\r\n									</div>\r\n									<a class=\"btn more_travel\" href=\"https://www.adpulsemedia.com/adpulse-media-features-technology/#section4\">More about retargeting</a>\r\n								</div>\r\n							</div>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        <!-- section 5 -->\r\n                        <div class=\"travelNetwork centerAlign greyback page_space AdDeisgn\" id=\"adDesign\">\r\n                                <a href=\"#adDesign\" class=\"scrollToTarget\">&nbsp;</a>\r\n                                <div class=\"wrapper\">\r\n                                    <h3 class=\"mtitle\">Ad Design</h3>\r\n                                    <!-- <div class=\"borderSec\"></div> -->\r\n                                    <div class=\"primiumContent\">\r\n                                        <h4>With better ads, you’ll